PDF uncertainties were computed fixing $\mu_F=\mu_R$=91 GeV and taking
different sets of the cteq6mE PDF in MCFM. Results for the sets giving
the largest variation of the cross-section ratio are shown in
Table~\ref{tab:mcfm_pdf_parameters}. 
