  \label{tab:mcfm_pdf_parameters}}
\begin{tabular}{|l|c|c|c|}
\hline
 & $\sigma(pp\rightarrow Z+b+X)$ (pb) & $\sigma(pp\rightarrow Z+j+X)$ (pb) &
  ${\cal R}$ \\
\hline
 PDF error set   8  & 2.92$\pm$0.01 & 68.1$\pm$0.3 & 0.043 \\
 PDF error set  29  & 3.08$\pm$0.01 & 68.8$\pm$0.3 & 0.045 \\
\hline
