Taking the largest deviation as uncertainty, the predicted value is:
\[
{\cal R}_{MCFM}=0.044^{+0.003}_{-0.002}.
\]
The largest variation of ${\cal R}$ is found when changing the
factorization scale $\mu_F$ from 91 GeV to 182 GeV.
